text: Ivan Enstad (born 20 April 1965) is a Norwegian rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Norwegian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Norway Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Tønsberg
